msgid "Meeting Integration"
msgstr "Besprechungsintegration"

msgid ""
"Zoom and Microsoft Teams meeting integration with company access control, "
"OAuth connections, personal meeting URLs, and activity meeting links."
msgstr ""
"Besprechungsintegration fuer Zoom und Microsoft Teams mit "
"Unternehmenszugangskontrolle, OAuth-Verbindungen, persoenlichen "
"Besprechungs-URLs und Aktivitaets-Besprechungslinks."

msgid ""
"Fixed MultipleObjectsReturned on the Zoom and Teams OAuth callbacks. "
"Improved the access-control UI: constrained the section to the viewport, "
"added a count + eye pill for allowed users and roles that opens a "
"HorillaListView modal, and fixed the card-wide click handler. Added "
"integration-settings view docstrings for pylint."
msgstr ""
"MultipleObjectsReturned in den Zoom- und Teams-OAuth-Callbacks behoben. "
"Zugangskontroll-UI verbessert und Indikatoren fuer erlaubte Benutzer und "
"Rollen hinzugefuegt. Docstrings fuer pylint-Konformitaet hinzugefuegt."

msgid ""
"Initial release: company-level meeting integration settings, Zoom and Teams "
"OAuth, per-user provider settings, MeetingLink CRUD, admin integration "
"screens under Settings → Integrations, My Settings entries, and generate-"
"link support for activities."
msgstr ""
"Erstveroeffentlichung: Besprechungsintegrationseinstellungen auf "
"Unternehmensebene, OAuth fuer Zoom und Teams, anbieterspezifische "
"Einstellungen pro Benutzer, MeetingLink-CRUD, Admin-Integrationsbildschirme "
"und Link-Generierungsunterstuetzung fuer Aktivitaeten."

